Tu zariya, Hoon main zariya,
Aur uski kitpaa dariya dariya,
 jo ankhiya nirmal,
Duniya nirmal,
Chhalka chhalka, chhal chhal chhal chhal

Ho zubaan koi bhi,
Bol dil se tu bol,
Ya misri si ho,
Ya shahad si ho.

Anti al umm,
Anti il hayaa,
Anti alhob,
Antilee alduna, anti lee aldunya.


Reedaha Reedaha,
Kefima reedaha,
Teflatan ya halee,
Wil asaal reegaha.
